            </div>
            <div class="card__title">Component Library</div>
            <div class="card__desc">A collection of common front-end code grouped together in components that can be shared and reused across multiple codebases, often with design, state, and default behavior built-in.
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="nys-grid-col-6 nys-desktop:nys-grid-col-3 nys-display-flex">
