              <img src="/assets/img/flex-card.svg" alt="flexdbox graphic">
            </div>
            <div class="card__title">Design Libraries</div>
            <div class="card__desc">
              A library of icons, styles, components, and variables that can be shared and reused across multiple design files for consistent design and prototyping.
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="nys-grid-col-6 nys-desktop:nys-grid-col-3 nys-display-flex">
